{"type": "article", "id": 53741, "title": "方圈圆环串起来的吊灯，像是一条珠宝项链｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-05-29T23:23:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 50685, "name": "Resident Studio"}, {"id": 35381, "name": "Kikkerland"}, {"id": 44164, "name": "Puma"}, {"id": 50686, "name": "MIT Design Lab"}, {"id": 39676, "name": "Sancal"}, {"id": 48806, "name": "Yonoh"}, {"id": 9999, "name": "Flos"}, {"id": 50687, "name": "Julie Hong"}, {"id": 17047, "name": "Michael Anastassiades"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 111, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180529191956WZXT1d7zHAvNru9J.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #dd4b39; -webkit-text-stroke: #dd4b39} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #dd4b39; -webkit-text-stroke: #dd4b39} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #dd4b39; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #dd4b39} span.s6 {font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} span.s7 {font-kerning: none; color: #dd4b39; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #dd4b39} span.s8 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none; color: #dd4b39; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #dd4b39} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Arrangements lighting collection by Michael Anastassiades for Flos</h3><p>土生土长的塞浦路斯设计师 Michael Anastassiades 与意大利灯饰大牌 Flos 已经合作过多次，在 4 月的米兰家具展上，他们一同推出了 Arrangements 照明系列，采用几何形状的 LED 灯条和圆环，结合在一起，可以做各种样式的吊灯。</p><p>Flos 将其描述为介于雕塑和工业设计品之间的作品，包括大大小小的正方形、圆环串联在一起，可以任意组合。Michael 称其灵感源自对于珠宝制作方式的兴趣，“它既是一条挂在脖子上的珠宝项链，也是一条从天花板上垂落而下的吊灯。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180529192027ysuiZ34UJYKeQc18.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.606808\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180529192028rDfkmFHjs2vEVw4c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180529192028l3J7byP1jcIxkWA8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665398\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180529192029HDtOVBUJKZLlIgd1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180529192029umt0gByDxzJWjkLa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180529192030tOYj40hs7ZRorz2P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/05/28/jewellery-chains-inspire-new-modular-lighting-system-by-michael-anastassiades-for-flos/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Mullit by Yonoh for Sancal</h3><p>西班牙家居设计工作室 Yonoh 今年与西班牙家具品牌 Sancal 深度合作，为其创作了很多系列产品。比如这款名为 Mullit 的座椅，看上去就是一个带着细细的椅腿的超软座垫，设计师的初衷就是想在椅子上复制软垫的舒适座感，又能够兼顾人体工程学的需求。</p><p>它看起来有点头重脚轻的不平衡感，但正是这种创造出来的反差感，赋予 Mullit 古灵精怪的个性。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=y0669cm7kqv&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180529192111ksW6Ycg8HSqrbjyC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180529192112oYStiGD2w7UJ4KBH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180529192112XtJcWaAOiNjpT0yv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180529192112x7VeJEbRK91jMWOA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.110000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180529192113eh8zwMfgqQ27FCHn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/mullit-cushion-legs-designed-yonoh-sancal/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Adaptive Dynamics: Biodesign by Puma and MIT Design Lab</h3><p>PUMA 与麻省理工学院设计实验室合作开展了一项实验设计，将生物学与运动服装结合在一起，打造了一套运动套装。双方将细菌透过专业技术融合在运动套装当中，带来 Breathing Shoes、Learning Insoles 和 Carbon-Eating T-Shirt 三样单品。</p><p>其中 Breathing Shoes 的鞋面充满细菌，穿着这双鞋的时候，其所产生的热能能够通过特殊的设计传导到 Learning Insoles，Learning Insoles 中的细菌对汗液产生化学反应，便能够通过精密仪器分析并且记录用户的身体变化及运动表现；而 Carbon-Eating T-Shirts 配有一颗小按钮，它含有对空气中的碳起反应的有机物，透过改变颜色来显示空气质量。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180529192210Aq5CWyHoDev2x7di.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562207\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180529192210RhBexXrLi2VSTHoN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667513\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180529192210YzU7BoVgAFnTuyZR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805291922115BrKt6P4spIve9y2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667513\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Wrap Bench by Julie Hong</h3><p>今年 4 月刚刚加入 Google 硬件团队的工业设计师 Julie Hong，她此前也曾自主设计生产过很多产品，比如这款 Wrap 长椅，属于办公环境和公共休闲区域之间的一种过渡产品。</p><p>在 Julie Hong 看来，千禧一代已经成长为上班族的主力人群，她想要把这个群体从过时的办公环境中解脱出来，Wrap 是其中一种尝试，让工作状态变得更加舒适，为同事间的沟通交流创造一个适宜环境。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180529192234uPgyk4qtmWnxGDMs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180529192234rj5nHQRpyADsFK1C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180529192234bLV0REWIXB2vA9a3.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180529192235g59Py4avp3TdZAmR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180529192235YtsaLeZFh6fcUxW7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180529192235gj0BbClFVwOWyRYk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Kikkerland Writersblok Bookmark Pen by Gerhardt Kellermann and Ana Relvao</h3><p>无论你正在阅读一本书或是在写作，美国创意生活用品设计品牌 Kikkerland 推出的这款书签笔，都是一款非常方便的小工具。</p><p>这支笔出自设计师 Gerhardt Kellermann 和 Ana Relvao 之手，它较为扁平的椭圆笔身使其易于抓握，也更方便夹在书页或是笔记本中，用作书签也不错。椭圆状的笔身使其不会从书页中滑落，如果要挑一个缺点的话，就是笔尖是一直暴露在外面的，不能缩回，也没有笔盖。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180529192306CvR8hjJ6VmdXeEOs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180529192306faoOBZGNldU9E17T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180529192307cpz5IH9LZ6S31Fwj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180529192307tlmgvXBY47KuNOZG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180529192307oYHBTe2hM3zu4xLc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805291923083vDyd971acequRJU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2018/05/25/the-pen-that-captures-ideas-and-holds-pages/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Circus Floor Light by Resident Studio</h3><p>Resident Studio 是新西兰一家创立于 2011 年的设计公司，Circus 落地灯是其推出的最新作品。它由 5 个相互连接的圆环组成，挂在一个十字灯架上，据称设计师的灵感源自珠宝展台以及女性梳妆台。</p><p>光源来自环环紧扣的圆形光环，360 度向外散发着温暖的光芒。不管是在商业空间还是家居空间，它都是一款不错的装饰性落地灯。售价 6690 欧元，<a href=\"https://resident.co.nz/lighting/floor-lights/circus-floor-light?color=brass\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180529192347bx6VXH8OB3gP15AG.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180529192348804O2fMguiyL6ReB.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}